Package com.comodide.axiomatization

Enum OWLAxAxiomType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<OWLAxAxiomType>
com.comodide.axiomatization.OWLAxAxiomType
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<OWLAxAxiomType>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum OWLAxAxiomType
extends java.lang.Enum<OWLAxAxiomType>
This is an enum containing all of the valid axiom types. It contains logic for getting the state of this enum and getting an OWLAxAxiomType from a string.
Author:
cogan
